{"tid":1459462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最近好想去旅行散下心","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:50:01.000Z","uid":85745,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00a344b1a9b64bcddab2198bee2360d64f6bc90c","tid":1459462,"uid":85745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"最近發夢發得太多, 好想出下門口去散下心, 但係又未買機票喎, <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇黎好可能要係機場當場買機票啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去旅行帶個背囊好似唔係好夠喎, 話曬都要幫朋友買下手信<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶埋個喼去就最好啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有, 最好用埋手機<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當場去不同航空格下價先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最緊要記住, 買機票唔洗急嫁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔啱價, 咪聽日再黎過囉。</span></span>"},{"pid":"042dffe101b05f9de7067665d119a02f77c2739a","tid":1459462,"uid":85745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}